sequenceDiagram
    participant Queue as Channel queue
    participant Worker as Gateway worker loop
    participant Identity as Identity and persona resolution
    participant Core as Core dispatcher
    participant Data as Data-access APIs
    participant LLMAdapter as LLM adapter
    participant LLM as LLM service
    participant Tool as Tool subprocess
    participant Recorder as Signal recorder

    Worker->>Queue: claim_inbound(gateway_id, lease_ttl)
    alt inbound ready
      Queue-->>Worker: inbound_message(channel_id, bot_account_id, peer_id, text, attachments)
      Worker->>Identity: resolve(channel, bot_account_id, peer_id)
      alt bound peer
        Identity-->>Worker: (user_id, persona_slug)
        Worker->>Core: dispatch(invocation, persona_slug)
        Core->>Data: query_memory(persona_slug, request)
        Data-->>Core: memory_context
        Core->>Data: load_active_tool_manifest(persona_slug, budget)
        Data-->>Core: tool_manifest(from_reviewed_tool_md)
        loop until final model turn
          Core->>LLMAdapter: complete(prompt, memory_context, tool_manifest)
          LLMAdapter->>LLM: provider_request(messages, tools)
          LLM-->>LLMAdapter: provider_response(content, tool_calls)
          LLMAdapter-->>Core: model_turn(content, tool_calls)
          opt LLM requested tool call
            Core->>Tool: execute_requested_tool(tool_name, args, env)
            Tool-->>Core: tool_result(exit_code, stdout, stderr)
          end
        end
        Core->>Recorder: record_signal(invocation, result, success_tags)
        Recorder->>Data: insert_signal(persona_slug, signal)
        Core-->>Worker: dispatch_result(reply)
        Worker->>Queue: enqueue_outbound(channel_id, peer_id, reply)
        Worker->>Queue: ack_inbound(message_id)
      else unbound peer
        Identity-->>Worker: binding_missing
        Worker->>Queue: mark_inbound_dead_letter(message_id, binding_missing)
      end
    else no inbound ready
      Queue-->>Worker: none
    end
    Note over Queue,Worker: Durable queue decouples external channel availability from Typhoon Way's agent loop.
    Note over Worker,Recorder: Core is the only caller that drives signal recording.
